      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "##  Better support for themes ⚫⚪ \r\n\r\nI updated the **default colors for the dark themes.** The old ones were atrocious I have no idea what was I thinking. 😅 \r\n\r\nI also made sure that the note colors will **update dynamically when the theme changes.** This fix also made it so that the popups and modals will have the base color and not the sticky note color, which I think looks better in my opinion. I included a screenshot.\r\n\r\n### OLD\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1c71cc3e-a976-4c4d-8fe7-fa20ab68a0b4)\r\n\r\n### NEW\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/6d1f9b96-10b4-47c8-976d-678cc519712e)\r\n",
