      "description": "## Added Color Settings 💃 🎉\r\n\r\nI finally found time to work on the plugin, (I have a vacation from work). And I am happy that I did work on it, I like how the color settings turned out to be 🙌 \r\n\r\nAgain, thanks @tu2-atmanand for essentially providing the code, inspiration and the idea to store colors in the frontmatter of each note.\r\n\r\nAlso, I was checking the plugin recently and there was over 1000+ downloads, which is pretty shocking given that I did no social media or announcement whatsoever. I guess people are randomly stumbling upon it.\r\n\r\nNext Release will mainly include bugfixes, so that we can finally reach a stable v1 release.",
